This is a PHP-based website which allows users to share comments and ratings on 
gay-themed movies.

In particular, the following features are supported:

 - login via Facebook so that users can share with their FB friends
 - Indicate movies that you've seen, rate them, and provide short 
   comments on them.
 - Go to IMDB and Amazon links for the movies
 - Sort movies by various ratings including selected FB friend, your ranking,
   IMDB, flixster and a combined rating.



